CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Classover Holdings, Inc. is a U.S.-based educational technology company specializing in interactive online live courses for K-12 students both domestically and internationally. Classover focuses on fostering essential skills such as creativity and problem-solving through its innovative courses, which range from interest-driven classes to competitive test preparation.
